name: jrexG.1
description:
Jrex is known as the lone assassin in the binary solar system. He was trained by the old Mohex sect. No one can match his speed in battle. His reputation is known throughout the galaxy, but no one knows his face. He only works for the Great Kingdom.
Name : Jrex
Tribe : Mohex
Planet : Shining Star
Weapon of Choice: Arrow
Religeon: Believes in the gods of Mohex
